capita than we do.

00:25:53.770 --> 00:25:55.950 align:middle line:84%
And so in the modern
world and what

00:25:55.950 --> 00:25:58.860 align:middle line:84%
we would still call a
very first-world nation,

00:25:58.860 --> 00:26:01.780 align:middle line:84%
there's people living very
differently than we do.

00:26:01.780 --> 00:26:05.010 align:middle line:84%
