00:26:36.630 --> 00:26:38.290 align:middle line:90%
and meaningful to them.

00:26:38.290 --> 00:26:42.270 align:middle line:84%
So there's a whole
range of different ways

00:26:42.270 --> 00:26:44.160 align:middle line:90%
